member.summary:
Change Sub Account USDT- Futures Commission Adjustment
This request will change the USDT- futures commission for a sub account
You need to enable "trade" option for the api key which requests this endpoint
The sub-account's USDT- futures commission of a symbol equals to the base commission of the symbol on the sub-account's fee tier plus the commission adjustment
If futures disabled, it is not allowed to set subaccount's USDT- futures commission adjustment on any symbol
member.param: The receive window for which this request is active. When the request takes longer than this to complete the server will reject the request
member.returns: Sub account USDT- futures commission result
